<div class="field field--display_title">
  <h2>More information</h2>
</div>
</h3>
            <div class="rich-text-wrapper">
          <p>If you have questions about leaving a gift to WWF in your Will take a look at our frequently asked questions:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/sites/default/files/2018-07/WWF%20FAQs.pdf">Download our Frequently Asked Questions&nbsp;(PDF)</a></li>
</ul>
<p><span lang="EN-US"><span><span>Or to speak to someone here about making or updating your will, call Grace or Ella on <strong>01483 412 153 </strong>or email </span></span></span><span lang="EN-US"><span><span><a href="mailto:stewardship@wwf.org.uk">stewardship@wwf.org.uk</a></span></span></span></p>


