            <h3>

<div class="field field--display_title">
  <h2>Information for Solicitors and Lay/Personal Representatives</h2>
</div>
</h3>
            <div class="rich-text-wrapper">
          <p><span><span><span><span>For further information about dealing with a Will and Estate for a client or a loved one, please contact our Legacy Administration Team. </span></span></span></span></p>
<p>Tel no. 01483 412247 or <a href="https://www.wwf.org.uk/form/legacy-executor-enquiry-form">email us</a>.</p>


      </div>
          </div>
</section>



  </div>

</article>

  </div>

  </span>

    
</main>

